{"tid":1691893,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點令人安心罷工?  整一份支持/清算罷工清單","createTime":"2019-11-04T00:08:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T13:10:22.000Z","uid":105976,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"08c40be66f7758cb778bcb101dffb4d4d9838b25","tid":1691893,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T00:08:42.000Z","msg":"出一份罷工公司名單<br />\n分為:<br />\n(A) 讚成罷工 (爆買) ,   (B)  中立,   (C) 清算罷工員工 (罷買&amp;基金支援員工)<br />\n<br />\n咁D公司會有誘因去支持, or至少唔敢清算員工<br />\n<br />\nd人最驚係俾公司清算   <br />\n1. 首先要令d公司唔咁去清算員工<br />\n2. 即使被清算都有保障"},{"pid":"c8328730f6a49bb97e39079b5d8717e3a6e4299b","tid":1691893,"uid":1241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T00:09:32.000Z","msg":"C  貼通告裝修<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15d5914f85b5a1eda521dd861b1bd55244e5329a","tid":1691893,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T00:14:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f12be0ebde894a80531dca4071e43e479fb9f1b","tid":1691893,"uid":295452,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T00:16:24.000Z","msg":"Good morning sir <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06a4c59ec6a6a42999cb07dbfa43a4e2fb0775bc","tid":1691893,"uid":288304,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T00:16:43.000Z","msg":"其實唔清算已經好足夠<br />\n<br />\n佢為公司好難直接表態支持<br />\n<br />\n我公司就提醒要維持基本運動，提醒每個部門要有一個人去應該查詢同緊急情況，即人處理唔到唔緊要但要有人理果種<br />\n<br />\n另外仲提醒大家公司一日病假係唔使射波紙，但都要跟手續入返record<br />\n<br />\n其實咁已經幫到盡"},{"pid":"25639dd63827c5be8f6cc2c35fddab9476dcd8ad","tid":1691893,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f12be0ebde894a80531dca4071e43e479fb9f1b","tid":1691893,"uid":295452,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T00:16:24.000Z","msg":"Good morning sir <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj